    "body": "### Summary\r\n\r\nCurrent documentation for `ActiveSupport::Cache#fetch_multi` method reads:\r\n\r\n`Options are passed to the underlying cache implementation.`\r\n\r\nBut does not provides an example.\r\nAlso, given that the method argument signature says (*names) is difficult to understand, without looking at the source code, how to pass options to this method.\r\n\r\nI have updated the documentation added an example on how to do this.\r\n"
