    "body": "### Summary\r\n\r\nActiveStorage gives you decent errors in rails log. However, the same is not true in case of Direct Uploads. There are no errors in rails log. Hence, this PR aims to start logging the errors in browser console for a better debugging experience. \r\n\r\n### Other Information\r\nWithout Logging:\r\n<img width=\"1528\" alt=\"app\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/235844/46259170-5790bb00-c4f3-11e8-9241-b2e0f45de03e.png\">\r\n\r\nWith Logging:\r\n<img width=\"1521\" alt=\"banners_and_alerts_and_app\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/235844/46259151-3760fc00-c4f3-11e8-8c1f-5534a4e52c3e.png\">\r\n\r\nLet me know if you agree with this approach?\r\n"
